title: Chicken Schnitzels & Herby Mash  with Garlicky Veggies & Hollandaise | Top Rated
description: Here's a neat trick: when you're crumbing food, use one hand for the wet ingredients and the other for the dry so you don't end up with fingers that look like dagwood dogs! Give it a try when you make these golden chicken schnitzels.
